      <akn:section eId="sec_1_308_02">
        <akn:num>1-308.02</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>PILOT agreements.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_1-308_02_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p></akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_1-308_02_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p></akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_1-308_02_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Notwithstanding any of the provisions of this part, a PILOT agreement shall not result in a reduction of the total assessed value of real property subject to taxation under Chapter 8 of Title 47.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_1-308_02_d">
      <akn:num>(d)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>A PILOT Agreement shall be an encumbrance upon, and run with, the PILOT Parcel. A memorandum of the PILOT Agreement shall be recorded in the land records of the District.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
